			</h1>
				<p style="text-align: left;"></p><div class="clearfix"><div class="about-column about-column-1"><img class="size-full wp-image-25 aligncenter" src="https://www.monkkee.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/pencil.png" alt="pencil" width="175" height="175"><p></p>
<p><!--
