--></p>
<h2 align="CENTER">Keep an online journal</h2>
<p><!--
P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; }
--></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">You want to keep your thoughts in a place where no one can find them? Or capture great ideas so they do not get lost? The online diary monkkee offers you a safe place for your very personal topics.</p></div><div class="about-column about-column-2">
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-full wp-image-92 aligncenter" src="https://www.monkkee.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/private.png" alt="private" width="175" height="175"></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Secret and private</h2>
<p><!--
P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; }
--></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">The use of monkkee is private only. There is no feature to make entries publicly viewable.&nbsp;This ensures that your secret diary remains safe from prying eyes. Just like in a good old paper diary.</p></div><div class="about-column about-column-3"><img class="size-medium wp-image-24 aligncenter" src="https://www.monkkee.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/lock.png" alt="lock" width="175" height="175"><p></p>
<p><!--
P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; }H3 { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; }H3.cjk { font-family: "SimSun"; }H3.ctl { font-family: "Mangal"; }
--><!--
P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; }H3 { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; }H3.cjk { font-family: "SimSun"; }H3.ctl { font-family: "Mangal"; }
--></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Secure and encrypted<strong><strong><br>
</strong></strong></h2>
<p><!--
P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; }A:link {  }
--></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">To guarantee you ultimate security, monkkee uses a comprehensive security concept. Client-side encryption, AES, SSL â€“ find out more about <a title="Security" href="https://www.monkkee.com/en/#security">security</a> and why monkkee is unique.</p></div><div class="about-column about-column-4"><img class="size-full wp-image-23 aligncenter" src="https://www.monkkee.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/cloud.png" alt="cloud" width="175" height="175"><p></p>
<p><!--
