			</h1>
				<p>Keep a private journal securely on the Internet â€“ to provide a convenient user experience your personal online diary monkkee offers you a variety of featuresâ€¦ and itâ€™s free!</p>
<div class="clearfix"><div class="features-column-image"><img class="size-full wp-image-104 aligncenter" src="https://www.monkkee.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/pocket_knife.png" alt="pocket_knife" width="225" height="225"><p></p>
